Effective Date: December 2025

Vaulty Safe (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how your data is handled when you use our mobile application.

⸻

1. Information We Collect

Vaulty Safe does not require account registration and does not collect any personally identifiable information such as name, email address, phone number, or location.

The application only stores the following data locally on your device:
	•	Income and expense records
	•	Transaction descriptions and categories
	•	Budget limits
	•	Selected currency and language
	•	App security preferences (such as PIN lock)

This data is stored only on your device and is never transmitted to any server.

⸻

2. How Your Data Is Used

Your data is used exclusively to:
	•	Display your balance
	•	Calculate reports and charts
	•	Manage your budget
	•	Protect your content with PIN security

Vaulty Safe does not use your data for advertising, analytics, or tracking purposes.

⸻

3. Data Sharing

We do not share, sell, rent, or trade any user data with third parties.
All data remains strictly private and stored on your device.

⸻

4. Data Security

Vaulty Safe uses device-level security and optional PIN protection to keep your financial information secure.
However, please note that no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

You are responsible for:
	•	Keeping your device secure
	•	Remembering your PIN code
	•	Backing up your data (if applicable)

⸻

5. Children’s Privacy

Vaulty Safe does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13.
If you believe that a child has provided personal data, please contact us immediately.

⸻

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be reflected on this page with a new effective date.

⸻

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, you may contact us at:

Email: 6353ww@gmail.com


